oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jimmie Rodger's Rejects Tape 2 of 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recordings are of a variety of studio recordings of Jimmie Rodgers (musician). Rodgers is accompanied by the Carters (musical group). Additionally, the dates of recording are unidentified. The tracks are labeled as rejected takes by Jimmie Rodgers. The tape is part two of two.
